# Quickstart: Validate Feature 002

Use this checklist to validate end-to-end:

1) Branding update
- Update title and/or upload valid image (square; 1400–3000 px; JPEG/PNG; RGB)
- Confirm RSS feed reflects changes
- Within 24h, confirm podcast app shows updated title/image
- Confirm future YouTube videos use updated metadata/thumbnail defaults (per‑video scope)

2) Health checks
- GET /health/youtube → status, message, lastSuccessAt present
- GET /health/doc-ingest → status, message, lastSuccessAt present
- GET /heartbeat → status + timestamp present

3) iOS Shortcut E2E (dry-run)
- Run the Shortcut’s dry‑run validation flow on device
- Confirm local validation OK and heartbeat shows OK

4) Script & Voice
- Generate an episode → verify structure, 12–20 min target, tone “Energetic, conversational, and warm”
- Select a voice style → preview plays
- Force preferred voice unavailable → fallback applied and communicated
